description.narrative: Nutrition(06)Technical Assistance to multiple Result Areas(RR,OR),which contributes to Adolescent Health And Nutrition, Prevention Of Stunting And Other Forms Of Malnutrition, Treatment Of Severe Acute Malnutrition. UNICEF aims to achieve this through Advocacy And Public Engagement, Operational Support To Programme Delivery, Systems Strengthening And Institution Building. This contributes to the following Country Programme result: Every Child to Survive and Thrive By 2021, countries apply child-sensitive policies, innovative community-centered approaches and evidence, to implement development and humanitarian interventions at scale, that enable Every Child to Survive and Thrive
